snippet.title: Top 99 2014: 33 Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Please watch: "The 10 Hottest Sex Positions Ranked By YOU" 
➨ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BkRFntsbb8k
-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-

Amber Heard has never been afraid to go full bombshell. From The Rum Diary (where she met her fiancé, Johnny Depp) to the upcoming Three Days To Kill (opposite Kevin Costner), she holds the camera like few of her peers. We also appreciate how frank she is in discussions of her sexuality.
